  "keyFeatures": [
    "ACID transaction-based MySQL to DuckDB replication",
    "Sequential Appender architecture (60,000+ rows/sec)",
    "Multi-database support with isolated replicas",
    "CDC binlog streaming for sub-second replication",
    "WebSocket SDK with 5-15ms query latency",
    "MySQL wire protocol server (port 3307)",
    "Automated sync, backups, and health monitoring",
    "S3 cloud backups with client-side encryption",
    "Query governor and read replicas",
